sequenceDiagram
    participant CB as Cán bộ xã
    participant API as Express API
    participant SVC as HouseholdService
    participant AUD as AuditService
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant MG as MongoDB

    Note over CB,MG: LUỒNG UC02 — CẬP NHẬT HỘ GIA ĐÌNH

    CB->>API: PUT /api/households/:id
    API->>API: Verify JWT + RBAC
    API->>SVC: updateHousehold(id, newData)

    SVC->>PG: SELECT * FROM households WHERE id = ?
    PG-->>SVC: oldData (snapshot hiện tại)

    SVC->>PG: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    SVC->>PG: UPDATE households SET ... WHERE id = ?
    SVC->>PG: UPDATE members SET ... (nếu có)
    SVC->>PG: COMMIT

    SVC->>AUD: logChange(id, oldData, newData, userId)
    AUD->>MG: INSERT audit_logs { action, oldData, newData, diff, timestamp }

    SVC-->>API: { success, household }
    API-->>CB: 200 OK

    Note over CB,MG: LUỒNG UC05 — TÁCH HỘ (2 DB cùng lúc)

    CB->>API: POST /api/households/:id/split
    API->>SVC: splitHousehold(sourceId, memberIds, newHeadId)

    SVC->>PG: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    SVC->>PG: INSERT INTO households (hộ mới)
    SVC->>PG: UPDATE members SET householdId = newId WHERE id IN (...)
    SVC->>PG: UPDATE households SET status = DA_TACH WHERE id = sourceId
    SVC->>PG: INSERT INTO household_relations (SPLIT record)
    SVC->>PG: COMMIT

    SVC->>AUD: logSplit(sourceId, newId, memberIds, userId)
    AUD->>MG: INSERT audit_logs { action: SPLIT, sourceId, newId, members }

    SVC-->>API: { sourceHousehold, newHousehold }
    API-->>CB: 200 OK

    Note over CB,MG: LUỒNG UC16 — ZALO TRA CỨU

    participant ZU as Người dân Zalo
    ZU->>API: POST /webhook (Zalo message)
    API->>SVC: handleZaloMessage(userId, text)

    SVC->>MG: GET zalo_sessions WHERE userId = ?
    MG-->>SVC: currentState (IDLE / AWAIT_QUERY / ...)

    SVC->>PG: SELECT households JOIN members WHERE name LIKE ?
    PG-->>SVC: results[]

    SVC->>MG: UPDATE zalo_sessions (state transition)
    SVC->>MG: INSERT zalo_events (log tra cứu)

    SVC-->>API: replyMessage
    API->>ZU: Zalo API sendMessage()
